    <h2>About CodePen</h2>

    <p>CodePen is little one-page app for playing around with front end code. Enter HTML, CSS, and JavaScript and the combined result is displayed below. This is extremely useful for showing off demos, troubleshooting, demonstrating bugs, or anything else you can think of.</p>

    <h2>CodePen is Open Source</h2>

    <p>Which means you can:</p>

    <ul>
      <li><a href="https://github.com/CodePen/CodePen/">Fork it on GitHub</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://github.com/CodePen/CodePen/issues?sort=created&direction=desc&state=open">Submit issues</a></li>
      <li>Pretty much do whatever you want with it, including install it on your own server.</li>
    </ul>

